original_title: Cue' Yoo / La pared / The Wall
overview: A photographic interpretation of Irma Pineda's poem "Cue' Yoo / La pared (The Wall)" that emphasizes how emotion etches itself on our memories, creating narratives that seep beyond expected boundaries of time and space. Translated to English by Wendy Call.
title: Cue' Yoo / La pared / The Wall
